  "detailed_description": "<strong><i>Wakey Wakey </i></strong> is a Puzzle Platformer with a unique world-bending twist. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/4917d458f1ebe488fb091498a1edccbc.poster.avif?t=1765928290\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/4917d458f1ebe488fb091498a1edccbc.webm?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/4917d458f1ebe488fb091498a1edccbc.mp4?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Navigate your everchanging bedroom, take control of new household objects, and overcome surprising obstacles to help this sleepy guy get a good night's rest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/36db5185a5d89395b22c57a9520bca92.poster.avif?t=1765928290\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/36db5185a5d89395b22c57a9520bca92.webm?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/36db5185a5d89395b22c57a9520bca92.mp4?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It's late at night and you wake up to find yourself laying down on the floor. <br><br>Somehow you must have rolled out of bed. <br><br>Better walk across your room so you can get some sleep. <br><br>Just when you're about to drift off, you open your eyes to find yourself on the floor again, <br><br>but something seems... <i>different</i>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/2f61f545b427c79520c7ac4bf6ea2268.poster.avif?t=1765928290\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/2f61f545b427c79520c7ac4bf6ea2268.webm?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/2f61f545b427c79520c7ac4bf6ea2268.mp4?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WAKEY WAKEY FEATURES</h2></u></i></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Puzzle Platformer</strong> where your main goal is to traverse the world of your bedroom<br><br></li><li>Take <strong>control of various objects</strong> around your room to aid you in your sleepy journey<br><br></li><li>Encounter surprising, <strong>world bending levels</strong>, that will make you wonder what's next<br><br></li><li>Complete <strong>challenging achievements</strong> to unlock fancy <strong>new outfits</strong> for your sleepy guy<br><br></li><li>Compete on <strong>local and global leaderboards</strong> and race your friend to complete levels as quickly as possible<br><br></li><li>Discover <strong><i>Nightmare Mode</i></strong>...<br><br></li><li>Try your best to <strong>get to the bed</strong> and get some rest</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/efa17c0fb37ac9920c00b284de7a3fbf.poster.avif?t=1765928290\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/efa17c0fb37ac9920c00b284de7a3fbf.webm?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/efa17c0fb37ac9920c00b284de7a3fbf.mp4?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><i>Wakey Wakey </i></strong> is a Puzzle Platformer with a unique world-bending twist. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/4917d458f1ebe488fb091498a1edccbc.poster.avif?t=1765928290\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/4917d458f1ebe488fb091498a1edccbc.webm?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/4917d458f1ebe488fb091498a1edccbc.mp4?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Navigate your everchanging bedroom, take control of new household objects, and overcome surprising obstacles to help this sleepy guy get a good night's rest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/36db5185a5d89395b22c57a9520bca92.poster.avif?t=1765928290\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/36db5185a5d89395b22c57a9520bca92.webm?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/36db5185a5d89395b22c57a9520bca92.mp4?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It's late at night and you wake up to find yourself laying down on the floor. <br><br>Somehow you must have rolled out of bed. <br><br>Better walk across your room so you can get some sleep. <br><br>Just when you're about to drift off, you open your eyes to find yourself on the floor again, <br><br>but something seems... <i>different</i>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/2f61f545b427c79520c7ac4bf6ea2268.poster.avif?t=1765928290\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/2f61f545b427c79520c7ac4bf6ea2268.webm?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/2f61f545b427c79520c7ac4bf6ea2268.mp4?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WAKEY WAKEY FEATURES</h2></u></i></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Puzzle Platformer</strong> where your main goal is to traverse the world of your bedroom<br><br></li><li>Take <strong>control of various objects</strong> around your room to aid you in your sleepy journey<br><br></li><li>Encounter surprising, <strong>world bending levels</strong>, that will make you wonder what's next<br><br></li><li>Complete <strong>challenging achievements</strong> to unlock fancy <strong>new outfits</strong> for your sleepy guy<br><br></li><li>Compete on <strong>local and global leaderboards</strong> and race your friend to complete levels as quickly as possible<br><br></li><li>Discover <strong><i>Nightmare Mode</i></strong>...<br><br></li><li>Try your best to <strong>get to the bed</strong> and get some rest</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/efa17c0fb37ac9920c00b284de7a3fbf.poster.avif?t=1765928290\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/efa17c0fb37ac9920c00b284de7a3fbf.webm?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047720/extras/efa17c0fb37ac9920c00b284de7a3fbf.mp4?t=1765928290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>"